templeInfo.history: Shri Siddhivinayak Temple is a Hindu temple dedicated to Lord Shri Ganesh. It is located in Prabhadevi, Mumbai, Maharashtra.
Shri Kashi Vishwanath Temple is one of the most famous Hindu temples dedicated to Lord Shiva. It is located in Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh.
Shri Mahalakeshwar Temple is an important Hindu temple dedicated to Mahakaal, a form of Shiva, in Ujjain, Madhya Pradesh, India.
Shri Jagannath Temple is an important Hindu temple dedicated to Jagannath, a form of Vishnu, in Puri, Odisha, India.
